<br>
I am also a heavy reader &amp; prolific poster on the &quot;official&quot; EQ boards in The Newbie Zone (Aimhian is my nick there, though I frequenly sign posts as I do here, with the one addition of the server name).  There, I frequently see the posting by a former player basically deriding those who still play calling them all sorts of names for doing so.  <br>
<br>
I completely forgot about the other group of people (the ones more likely to be -here- as opposed to only there), the ones who had to leave or chose to leave the game but not the community of friends.<br>
<br>
Firiona Vie -is- the most mature of the servers and the one with a -real- community <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->   I can easily see how one could leave the game but not the community here.<br>
